{
  "id": "69f7c4bc6579a16fe68c6f0e",
  "title": "2026/03/29―takker",
  "created": 1777845437,
  "updated": 1777845444,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69f7c4bc6579a16fe68c6f0e",
      "text": "2026/03/29―takker",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845437,
      "updated": 1777845437
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4bd0000000000a102f8",
      "text": "from [2026/03/29]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845437,
      "updated": 1777845437
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4bd0000000000a102f9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845437,
      "updated": 1777845441
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4bd0000000000a102fa",
      "text": "[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845437,
      "updated": 1777845437
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4bd0000000000a102fb",
      "text": " 研究室Slackの先生のアイコンかわいい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845437,
      "updated": 1777845437
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4bd0000000000a102fc",
      "text": " 大学来たらﾄｶﾁｬﾝがいた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845437,
      "updated": 1777845437
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4bd0000000000a102fd",
      "text": "  かわいいね",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845437,
      "updated": 1777845437
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4bd0000000000a102fe",
      "text": " 来年度の健康診断とか大学院から来た連絡とか見てる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845437,
      "updated": 1777845437
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4bd0000000000a102ff",
      "text": " 　大学の規模がおかしすぎてここのところずっと驚きまくってる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845437,
      "updated": 1777845437
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4bd0000000000a10300",
      "text": " 　使い切れないレベルのリソースが提供されている、どうなってんだよここの厚生施設",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845437,
      "updated": 1777845437
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4bd0000000000a10301",
      "text": " 　少しは理科大に分けろ、土地広すぎだろ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845437,
      "updated": 1777845437
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4bd0000000000a10302",
      "text": " 　転学したんか[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845437,
      "updated": 1777845437
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4bd0000000000a10303",
      "text": " 　そういえばちゃんと井戸端で書いてなかったかも[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845437,
      "updated": 1777845437
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4bd0000000000a10304",
      "text": " 　 [2025/09/05#68ba9d890000000000f26571]で受かった大学院に進学することを選びました",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845437,
      "updated": 1777845437
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4bd0000000000a10305",
      "text": " 学会発表の概要を書く",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845437,
      "updated": 1777845437
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4bd0000000000a10306",
      "text": " 　大学院の先生にアドバイスもらって方針明確になった。よかった",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845437,
      "updated": 1777845437
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4bd0000000000a10307",
      "text": " 　卒論で十分、すこし概要に手を加えるだけ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845437,
      "updated": 1777845437
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4bd0000000000a10308",
      "text": " 　今日中になんとかする",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845437,
      "updated": 1777845437
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4bd0000000000a10309",
      "text": " 情報が多すぎる！",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845437,
      "updated": 1777845437
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4bd0000000000a1030a",
      "text": "  シラバスもまだみれてないんだが",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845437,
      "updated": 1777845437
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4bd0000000000a1030b",
      "text": "  いったん概要作成を優先しよう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845437,
      "updated": 1777845437
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4bd0000000000a1030c",
      "text": " 授業開始が来週なの今知った",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845437,
      "updated": 1777845437
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4bd0000000000a1030d",
      "text": "  やばいじゃん、なんも準備してない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845437,
      "updated": 1777845437
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4bd0000000000a1030e",
      "text": " ようやく学会の発表概要みたいなものを書く",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845437,
      "updated": 1777845437
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4bd0000000000a1030f",
      "text": "  卒論手直しで済むかと思っていたがそんなことはなかった",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845437,
      "updated": 1777845437
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4bd0000000000a10310",
      "text": "  LaTeXで時間食って何も考えていない気がする",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845437,
      "updated": 1777845437
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4bd0000000000a10311",
